Field Documentation

UInt32 Vps_DssDispcWbPipeConfig::cropEnable

Enable or Disable Crop (Region based writeback) Not applicable for TDA2XX.

UInt32 Vps_DssDispcWbPipeConfig::cscFullRngEnable

Full range or Limited Range for CSC module. For valid values check Vps_DssDispcCscRange.

UInt32 Vps_DssDispcWbPipeConfig::scEnable

Enable or disable the scaling, enable only if input size and Output size are different. For valid values check Vps_DssDispcScEnable.
